en_175101_0	A shooting incident was reported from a jewellery shop in Thalawathugoda this afternoon (02).
en_175101_1	At around 12.50 pm, two persons had attempted to rob a jewellery shop and then the owner of the shop had struggled with the robbers.
en_175101_2	The owner had a sharp object in his possession and then one of the robbers had opened fire.
en_175101_3	It had caused injuries to the shop owner and he was later hospitalized.
en_175101_4	In the meantime, the robbers have fled the scene.
